      <title>前汇丰交易员因经纪费用警报败诉，损失 140 万欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/ex-hsbc-trader-loses-1-4-million-lawsuit-over-high-brokerage-fees-alert</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司的一名前交易员声称，在他揭发银行向经纪公司支付的过高费用后，银行与他反目成仇。他在巴黎劳动法庭上败诉，要求赔偿 140 万欧元（合 140 万美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/ex-hsbc-trader-loses-1-4-million-lawsuit-over-high-brokerage-fees-alert</guid>
